A Joburg
resident who tried to bribe a City of Joburg official with R5000 will appear at
the Jobug Magistrate’s Court on Monday. The 32
year-old was arrested in Mayfair on Thursday after he tried to bribe an
official who was part of “Operation #BuyaMtheto.”#BuyaMtheto
was launched by the City of Joburg in an attempt to disconnect water and
electricity that has been connected illegally, and to enforce the City’s
